N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6053.1 - Juvenile arrest fingerprint card

State Regulations

Juvenile arrest information reported to DCJS shall be the
information required to be entered on form DCJS-2, juvenile arrest fingerprint
card. Notes
